An RLJ Entertainment company, Acorn Productions Limited manages and licenses the rights of eminent crime, mystery and drama brands, including TV series Foyle's War. We produce and co-produce TV and films based on the brands that we own and license the rights to publishing houses, theatrical producers, TV producers, games developers and digital businesses throughout the world.


 








