			Company Description 


			RLJ Entertainment, Inc. is an entertainment content distribution company, which engages in the distribution and licensing of entertainment content. It also operates channels under the Acorn, Acacia and Urban Movie Channel brands. The company was founded on April 2, 2012 and is headquartered in Silve...
		


                RLJ Entertainment, Inc. is an entertainment content distribution company, which engages in the distribution and licensing of entertainment content. It also operates channels under the Acorn, Acacia and Urban Movie Channel brands. The company was founded on April 2, 2012 and is headquartered in Silver Spring, MD.
            




